= Make a release:

== Pre-release:

* update docs
* Update copyright years if needed, in the following paths:
  + lib/*
* Check version in lib/hoe-packaging.rb
* Update History.rdoc
* git:manifest
* bundler:gemfile
* bundler:gemfile_lock
* bundle_audit:run
* git -a -m "Anything"
* git tag x.x.x

== Release:

* Create Release in Launchpad
* rake release
* send_email
* clean_pkg

== Post-release:

* Bump version
* Add new Milestone on Launchpad